flowchart TD
    A[Incoming query] --> B[Read SEARCH_BACKEND]
    B --> C[Register default search adapters]
    C --> D{Adapter exists?}
    D -- Yes --> E[Instantiate backend]
    D -- No --> F[Fallback to elasticsearch adapter]
    F --> E
    E --> G{Backend key}
    G -- elasticsearch --> H[Query Elasticsearch backend]
    G -- database --> I[Score records from registry relations]
    G -- pg_search --> J[Use pg_search scopes or database fallback]
    H --> K[Return SearchResult]
    I --> K
    J --> K
